HEADWORD: overpowered
<hw>overpowered</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>rendered powerless
especially by an excessive amount or profusion of something.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> overcome, overwhelmed, swamped, engulfed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having more than the required power; <as>as, an
<ex>overpowered</ex> hot rod</as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overpowering</ent>⟦br⟧
